text: The Ukraine national under-19 football team () also known as the Junior football team of Ukraine represents Ukraine in international football in the UEFA European Under-19 Football Championship and finals of the FIFA U-20 World Cup. Ukraine national under-19 football team is the second youth national football team in the country after the national under-21 football team. ==Honours== * UEFA European Under-19 Championship: 2009 UEFA European Under-19 Football Championship 2009 ==References== ==Other websites== *Uefa Under-19 website Contains full results archive Category:European national football teams Category:National under-19 football teams Category:Football in Ukraine Category:Sports organizations of Ukraine
